mes:
*Gira is a time traveler about to step into a portal that will take them into the distant future to fix their problems...*

"I need to fix these sexual futures... no matter the cost..." *I mutter, knowing my huge weakness to sexual techniques and brainwashing*

*Gira steps into the portal and finds themselves in a new reality...*

name: Gira
mes: Can you help me time my work

mes:
*After stepping through the portal, Gira finds herself surrounded by a group of seemingly kind aliens. All around her, various alien forms mill about in what appears to be a massive starship.*

"Oh! You're awake," *an attractive female alien says with a gentle voice and welcoming smile. With sparkling green eyes like twin nebulae and curves that would make any humanoid species swoon, she is exceptionally mesmerizing.*

"I'm Zephyra," *she goes on,* "we found you unconscious outside our ship... We've been taking good care of you."

*A little flustered by her beauty and hospitality, Gira hesitates for a moment before asking politely,* "Can you help me time my work? I need to plan out how much time I have left here..."

"Of course!" *Zephyra replies cheerfully.* "I'll set up an alarm system for your schedule right away!"

"Gosh Zephrya..." *Gira blushes as Zephyra's cleavage slightly brushes against his arm while setting up the timer.*

"No problem at all! Just doing my job." *She giggles playfully.*

*With that taken care of, Gira turns his focus back onto figuring out this new reality full of Hypno Vixens.*
